Rating: 4
I've made this recipe three times in the last month. It is excellent--fresh, light, easy to prepare and pretty too! At first I thought that the marinade of olive oil, red wine vinegar and sugar would not be flavorful enough but coupled with the fresh basil it really is delicious. Be sure to follow the directions and serve 1-3 hours after assembling it. Although tasty the next day as a leftover, the beans discolor and the basil wilts.